These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, cucumber
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, teacher
1. the mechanic is in an even position##4
2. the teacher is the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Food   | cucumber | raspberry |
| Job     | teacher    | mechanic   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, spanish
1. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee        |
| Nationality      | indonesian  | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
House: cottage, modern
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
2. the modern house is on the left of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| House   | modern    | cottage |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade
House: gothic-revival, palace
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the palace house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | 7up      | lemonade |
| House       | gothic-revival | palace    |

