.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, electronic
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, polish
1. the dutch is in an even position##4
2. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Music-Genre           | pop | electronic |
| Nationality   | polish    | dutch         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, rugby
2 different games are played: chess, domino
1. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | rugby | climbing  |
| Game   | domino  | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-7::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, sudoku
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, daisy
1. the person who growsdaisy is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | gardening   | sudoku     |
| Flower     | aconite | daisy |

