.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-10::.
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, corn
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, september
1. the person who's birthday is in september is the person eating corn##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |
| Food          | corn | blueberry |
| Birthday   | september | may   |

