.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, polish
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, chestnut
1. the polish is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the canadian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Nationality   | polish | canadian   |
| Color         | mauve | chestnut |

